透过这个手机屏中的微信群，从空中飞机俯瞰，一家姊妹兄弟五人组成的一个手掌，不知不觉中，五指并拢，形成了一个加油鼓劲的拳头……文 | 刘　放一面手机屏，能汇天下事。
Through the microphone screen, a hand made up of five sisterly brothers overlooks a cell phone screen. Unconsciously, the five fingers converge to form a cheering fist... Wen Fang has a cellphone screen that wraps up the world.
我们家的家族微信群，虽容纳面不算太大，却也差不多覆盖了小半个中国：姐姐是老大，守在老家湖北黄石；我排行老二，客居江东苏州三十年；弟弟老三，安家西南重庆永川；大妹老四，离老家不远，在汉口聆听百年江汉关的钟声；老五最远，跨南岭南下，远嫁特区香港。
Our family micro-faith group, although not too large, but almost cover half of China: my sister is the eldest sister, guarding their home in Huangshi, Hubei Province; my brother third, located in south-west Chongqing Yongchuan; Big Sister, not far from home, in Hankou listening to the hundred-year-old Jiang Han Guan.
平时的群里，家事国事天下事，风声雨声读书声，应有尽有，话题散漫，啥都能留文字。
Usually in the group, the family affairs of the world, the wind and rain to read the sound of books, everything, casual topics, anything can leave text.
有时偷懒不想掐字了，不愿费力卷起舌尖说普通话，就用方言哇啦几句。
Sometimes lazy do not want to pinch words, do not want to roll up the tip of the tongue to speak Mandarin, with a few words in dialect.
谁获得什么奖励，必定群里晾晒。
Whoever gets any reward must air it in the group.
谁脑洞大开有心得了，也少不得要群里发布，大家有空了七言八十讨论，畅叙高见。
Who can open the brain hole has the idea, also must not want the group to release, everyone has free seven-character-80 discussion, high-opinion.
甚至烧了一只什么好小菜，也要发张图片上来，让小小的家族群色香味俱全。
Even burned a good dish, but also send out a picture, so that the small family of color and fragrance.
大妹老四守在汉口猪年腊月廿九，农历年最后一个上班日，群里一下子风云突变。
Big sister four in Hankou pig year 29, the Chinese New Year last working day, a sudden change in the group.
武汉疫情发展快，为了控制疫情蔓延，武汉行壮士断腕之举，背水一战——封城。
Wuhan epidemic rapid development, in order to control the spread of the epidemic, Wuhan Zhuangshi action, back water - closed the city.
我发言。
I have the floor.
因为控制疫情最简单而有效的方法，就是及时切断蔓延的污染源。
Because the simplest and most effective way to control the epidemic is to cut off the spread of the pollution source in time.
要全国甚至全世界一盘棋意识，封城是无情中藏大爱。
Want the whole country or even the whole world to be aware of chess, the city is ruthless Tibet love.
大姐立刻发上一个两道绿泪长流的表情。
Sister immediately issued a long flow of two green tears expression.
四妹家大楼楼顶能望到收治新冠肺炎病人的同济医院。
Tongji Hospital for New Crown Pneumonia can be seen from the roof of the Sijie Building.
左边这栋黄色房子是同济医学院的学生公寓，中间那栋是同济医院外科楼，右边这栋是同济医院综合楼。
The yellow house on the left is the student apartment of Tongji Medical College. In the middle is the surgical building of Tongji Hospital and on the right is the Tongji Hospital Complex.
小妹却发上一支歌曲《东方之珠》。
My little sister sent out a song, Pearl of the Orient.
歌中唱：小河弯弯向东流，流到香江去看一看，东方之珠我的爱人，你的风采是否浪漫依然……弟弟发上的是一个额头流汗的表情图。
Sing in the song: River bend eastward flow, flow to Xiangjiang to see, Pearl of the Orient, my love, your style is still romantic... Brother hair is a brow sweaty emotive map.
他说：“香港的确不乏浪漫，但住房太挤。
"Hong Kong does have a lot of romance, but it's too crowded," he said.
内地人去旅游观光是可以的，却住不惯，让大姐和大妹两家都到香港，肯定不现实。
Mainland people can go sightseeing is possible, but not used to living, let the elder sister and sister both to Hong Kong, certainly unrealistic.
我投反对票。
I voted against it.
”我发一个大拇指的图，称赞：“‘重庆人’很理智，言之在理！”小妹再迅疾发上来一首诗，是戴望舒的《我用残损的手掌》。
"I sent out a thumbnail diagram and praised:" Chongqing people are very rational, the words are reasonable! "The younger sister then quickly sent out a poem, Dai Wangshu's" I use the damaged palm.
这首诗是抗日战争期间，诗人在香港参加抗日救亡运动，被投入监狱，受尽严刑拷打。
This poem is during the Anti-Japanese War, the poet participated in the Anti-Japanese War in Hong Kong, was put into prison, tortured.
获保释后，他摸着自己的遍体鳞伤，联想到祖国河山的破碎，怀着对侵略者的切齿痛恨和对祖国的无限爱怜，写下如泣如诉诗篇。
After being released on bail, he felt his wounds all over his body, remembered the breakup of the motherland, and wrote down his sobbing psalms with deep hatred for the invaders and boundless love for his country.
我理解小妹发这首诗的深意，她的“残损手掌”并不是指当下疫情肆虐的情势，而是将我们姊妹五个比喻成五个长短不一的手指，构成一只手掌。
I understand the meaning of the poem. Her "mutilated hand" does not refer to the current situation, but to compare our five sisters into five fingers of varying length, forming a hand.
如今手掌受伤，疼痛的是连心的十指。
Now palm injury, pain is connected with the ten fingers of the heart.
我发了个微笑表情。
I gave a smile.
为了不让气氛过于压抑，我在群中发的话有些“隔山打牛”。
In order not to suppress the atmosphere too much, I in the group of words some "hit the bull off the hill."
我引用李白的诗句：“故人西辞黄鹤楼，烟花三月下扬州”，说，过了扬州再扬帆，那就是苏州了。
I quote Li Bai's poem: "The Yellow Crane Tower in the West, the fireworks in Yangzhou in March," said that beyond Yangzhou, it is Suzhou.
我苏州的房子大，接待大姐和大妹两家根本不成问题。
I have a big house in Suzhou. There is no problem for my sister and my sister.
湖北送了苏州一个伍子胥，他象天法地、相土尝水建成了矗立两千多年不倒的古城，这古城最应该感激的就是湖北。
Hubei sent a Wu Tzu-shi in Suzhou. He made an ancient city that stood untoppled for more than two thousand years. Hubei is the most grateful city.
如今湖北有难，岂有不两肋插刀、慷慨接待之理？而且，让苏州名声大振的古诗《枫桥夜泊》，作者张继正是湖北襄阳人，到苏州听夜半钟声到客船，情调估计不会逊色多少江汉关的钟声。
In addition, the famous Suzhou poem The Night Park of Fengqiao, written by Zhang Xiangyang of Hubei Province, goes to Suzhou to listen to the bells of midnight to the passenger ships.
不信，实地听一听。
Believe it or not, listen to me.
年初十，刘放在单位弟弟说，到苏州的构想比到香港要务实得多，现实得多，苏州与湖北也的确有很深的渊源，是可行的方案之一。
Liu said that the concept of going to Suzhou is much more practical and realistic than going to Hong Kong. Suzhou and Hubei do have deep ties and are one of the feasible plans.
但苏州二哥是吃新闻饭的，忙得很，去了可不仅仅只是一个住宿的问题，还会有一连串的生活和工作等诸方面的一揽子工程要解决，就显得捉襟见肘了。
However, Suzhou Second Brother is eating the news, busy, go can not only be a problem of accommodation, there will be a series of life and work and other aspects of the package to solve, it seems to be overstretched.
不如再启动一套方案——到重庆。
How about starting a plan again - to Chongqing.
想当年，日本鬼子侵略中国，一时气焰嚣张，占领了大半个中国，但重庆就是一块他们死活啃不动的硬骨头。
Back then, the Japanese invading China, for a while arrogance, occupied most of China, but Chongqing is a hard bone they can not bite.
武汉是英雄城，重庆何尝不是英雄城？还怕它小小的病毒？到重庆来，我的房子比苏州的还大，而且我不是打工仔，我有自己的经济实体要打理，大姐和大妹若不嫌弃，在重庆可以帮助我经营，工作生活也一应俱全都得到妥善解决，这可是进能攻退能守的最佳方案。
Wuhan is a hero city, Chongqing is not a hero city? I am afraid it is a small virus? To Chongqing, my house is bigger than Suzhou, and I am not a wage-earner, I have my own economic entities to manage.
大姐此时破涕为笑，她说，即便武汉封城，她也有办法开车到汉口接大妹一家。
The elder sister smiled now, saying that even if Wuhan was closed, she would be able to drive to Hankou to pick up the girls.
她对武汉的路径熟悉，绕开高速出口，多走省道和不重要的路，可以轻而易举突围。
She is familiar with Wuhan route, bypass high-speed exits, take more provincial and unimportant roads, can easily break through.
大姐有驾驶大客的A照，驾驶技术出众，带出徒弟众多，其中不少徒弟的年纪比她还大很多。
The eldest sister has a driver A photo, driving skills, take out a lot of apprentices, many of whom are much older than her.
往常过年，给她拜年的徒弟碰巧就能凑成两桌。
It happened that the apprentice who paid her a New Year's call could make up two tables.
她对武汉周边的路线的确太熟悉了。
She really knows the route around Wuhan.
大妹笑笑，给大姐一个大拇指，说：简直可以称得上七进七出长坂坡的孤胆英雄女版赵子龙嘛！但是，武汉一千多万人民，你咋救？如果都想着外逃，外面容纳得了这么多人吗?大姐知道大妹说的是反话，一时无语，只能回应一个红脸流汗的表情。
She smiled and gave her a thumbs-up and said, "It's seven times better than the seven-step-sakamoto's heroine Zhao Zilong! But, Wuhan, more than 10 million people, how can you save? If you want to escape, the outside can accommodate so many people?
大妹继续说， 有一句哲言：雪崩时没有一片雪花是无辜的。
The eldest sister went on, a wise saying: In an avalanche not a single snowflake is innocent.
对这句话有许多种解读，也有许多出典，但用在面对疫情可能暴发之时，非常恰切。
There are many interpretations of this sentence, and there are many examples, but it is very appropriate when faced with the possibility of an outbreak.
再洁白无瑕的雪花，如果加入了雪崩行列，那这朵雪花瞬间就变色了，变成黑色或者红色。
If you add an avalanche to the white snow, the snowflake will instantly turn black or red.
大姐最懂汽油的原理，一个人身上着火了，屋外是汽油库，能带着身上的火往屋外跑吗？不能。
Big sister best understand the principle of gasoline, a person on fire, outside is a gasoline depot, can carry the fire to run out of the house? No.
最佳的办法，是就地趴下，迅速扑灭身上的火。
The best thing to do is to lie down and quickly put out the fire.
否则，外逃不但会造成引发疫情的罪人，自己也根本就跑不了。
Otherwise, the flight would not only create the culprits who caused the outbreak, but would not be able to escape.
大妹再亮出一个笑脸，说：“恐慌是一切愚蠢和低能的通病。
She smiled again and said, "Panic is a common fault of all stupidity and imbecility.
我也引用一首词来奉送诸位，显得咱略通文墨。
I also quote a word to give you, it appears that we are somewhat literate.
词曰：山下旌旗在望，山头鼓角相闻。
Words said: the mountain banners at the top of the drum sound.
敌军围困万千重，我自岿然不动。
I stood firm as the enemy besieged it.
早已森严壁垒，更加众志成城。
Strong barriers, more than ever.
黄洋界上炮声隆，报道病毒宵遁。
Artillery rumbles in the Yellow Sea to report the virus overnight.
”我点赞，好！好！好！词中将“敌军”改成“病毒”，准确生动，而这原本就是一场没有硝烟的战役。
"I would like to praise, good! Good! Good!" The word "enemy" was changed to "virus," accurate and vivid, and this was meant to be a battle without smoke.
人人都是战士，没有一个能成为旁观者。
Everyone is a fighter, and no one can be a spectator.
如果我没有理解错的话，老家的亲人不准备突围了？大妹说，大树巍然矗立，何必作鸟兽散？誓与大武汉共存亡！小妹说，好的好的，我们从香港、苏州、重庆三地，与全国人民一道，向老家的亲人空投物资，除了口罩等卫生用品，我们还会快递新鲜蔬菜。
If I am not mistaken, the family back home is not ready to break through? Big sister said, tree towering, why die together with the Great Wuhan! Yes, we will, together with the people from Hong Kong, Suzhou, Chongqing, air-drop supplies to relatives back home, besides masks and other sanitary materials, we will send fresh vegetables.
透过这个手机屏中的微信群，从空中飞机俯瞰，一家姊妹兄弟五人组成的一个手掌，不知不觉中，五指并拢，形成了一个加油鼓劲的拳头……四妹家阳台看小区本文图片均由受访者提供征集令《新民周刊》现面向全国征集新冠肺炎采访对象和真实故事：如果你是参与抗击新冠肺炎疫情的医护人员或其家属，我们希望聆听你的“战疫”故事，也希望传达你的诉求。
Through the microphone screen, looking down from the air, a sisterly five-brother palm, unwittingly, five fingers together to form a cheering fist...
如果你是确诊、疑似患者本人或家属，我们希望了解你和家人如何“抗疫”的过程，让外界了解你的真实经历。
If you are a confirmed, suspected patient or family member, we would like to know how you and your family have responded to the epidemic and let the outside world know about your true experience.
如果你是疫情严重地区的普通市民，我们希望展现你的乐观，并倾听你所需的帮助。
If you are an ordinary citizen of a highly affected area, we hope to show your optimism and listen to the help you need.
如果你是公共服务人员或各类捐助者，我们希望看到你的“最美逆行”，记录下你的无私。
If you are a public service provider or a variety of donors, we want to see your "most beautiful retrograde" and record your selflessness.
……抗击新冠肺炎疫情，我们诚征对疫情了解的社会各界人士，提供相关线索，说出你的故事，让我们用新闻留存这一切。
To fight the New Crown Pneumonia epidemic, we sincerely invite all sectors of the community to understand the epidemic, provide relevant clues, tell your story, let us use the news to retain all this.
